  <para style="h">Abafiripi</para>
  <para style="toc1">Ebbaluwa ya Pawulo Omutukuvu eri Abafiripi</para>
  <para style="toc2">Abafiripi</para>
  <para style="toc3">Baf</para>
  <para style="mt2">Ebbaluwa ya Pawulo Omutukuvu eri</para>
  <para style="mt1">Abafiripi</para>
  <para style="imt">Ennyanjula</para>
  <para style="ip">Omuwandiisi w’ebbaluwa eno ye Pawulo Omutukuvu. Yagiwandiikira Ruumi ng’ali mu busibe, wakati w’emyaka <char style="sc">ad</char> 58 ne 64. Yagiwandiikira mikwano gye abaagalwa ennyo abaali mu kibuga Firipi eky’omu Makedoniya (kaakano eyitibwa Buyonaani). Omulamwa gw’ebbaluwa eno bwe bulamu obujjudde emikisa gya Katonda, omuntu bw’afuna nga buyita mu Yesu Kristo. Abeebaza olw’okumuweereza ensimbi ez’okumuyamba mu byetaago bye. Asookera ku kubategeeza nga bw’abeesiga, n’alyoka abamanyisa ebimu ku bizibu by’alina mu Ruumi. Abannyonnyola nti singa afa mu kiseera ekyo, ajja kutenderezanga mu maaso ga Kristo. Era ne bw’asigalawo nga mulamu, ajja kwongera okuweereza Katonda n’amaanyi ge gonna nga bw’asobola. Akuutira Abafiripi okugobereranga obwetoowaze bwa Kristo n’obutakkiririzanga mu bayigiriza ab’obulimba. Waaliwo abakyala babiri abooluganda nga bayombagana, n’abanenya era n’abalagira basonyiwagane. Abakkiriza bonna abakuutira babeerenga bawombeefu, nga bassa kimu, era nga balina amaanyi aga Mwoyo Mutukuvu; abantu ab’empisa ennungi, abalina emirembe n’essanyu mu buli mbeera yonna, oba nnungi, oba mbi. Kubanga Katonda anaabawanga byonna bye beetaaga mu bulamu bwabwe.</para>
  <para style="ie"/>
  <chapter number="1" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Okulamusa</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:1 a </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ACT 16:1">Bik 16:1</ref>; <ref loc="2CO 1:1">2Ko 1:1</ref> </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">b </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ACT 9:13">Bik 9:13</ref> </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">c </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ACT 16:12">Bik 16:12</ref> </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">d </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1TI 3:1">1Ti 3:1</ref> </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">e </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1TI 3:8">1Ti 3:8</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nze Pawulo ne Timoseewo abaddu ba Kristo Yesu tuwandiikira abatukuvu bonna mu Kristo Yesu abali mu Firipi, awamu n’abalabirizi n’abadiikoni; <verse number="2" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:2 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 1:7">Bar 1:7</ref></char></note>ekisa n’emirembe ebiva eri Katonda Kitaffe ne Mukama waffe Yesu Kristo, bibeerenga nammwe.</para>
  <para style="s1">Okwebaza n’okusaba Katonda</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:3 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ROM 1:8">Bar 1:8</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nneebaza Katonda wange buli lwe mbajjukira, <verse number="4" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:4 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 1:10">Bar 1:10</ref></char></note>era buli lwe mbasabira mwenna nsaba nga nzijudde essanyu. <verse number="5" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:5 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 2:42">Bik 2:42</ref>; <ref loc="PHP 4:15">Baf 4:15</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 16:12-40">Bik 16:12-40</ref></char></note>Kubanga okuviira ddala ku lunaku olwasooka n’okutuusiza ddala kaakano mwetaba wamu nange mu njiri. <verse number="6" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:6 </char><char style="xt" closed="false">nny 10; <ref loc="1CO 1:8">1Ko 1:8</ref></char></note>Nkakasiza ddala nti oyo eyatandika omulimu omulungi mu mmwe, aligutuukiriza okutuusa ku lunaku lwa Kristo Yesu. <verse number="7" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:7 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2PE 1:13">2Pe 1:13</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2CO 7:3">2Ko 7:3</ref></char></note>Kino kituufu okubalowoozaako bwe ntyo mwenna, kubanga mundowoozaako mu kusibibwa kwange ne mu kulwanirira Enjiri, ne mu kuginyweza, nga mwenna mwetaba wamu nange mu kisa. <verse number="8" style="v"/>Katonda ye mujulirwa wange nga mwenna bwe mbaagala n’okwagala okuva eri Kristo Yesu. <verse number="9" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:9 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1TH 3:12">1Bs 3:12</ref></char></note>Mbasabira nti okwagala kwammwe kweyongerenga, era mujjule amagezi n’okutegeera, <verse number="10" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:10 </char><char style="xt" closed="false">nny 6; <ref loc="1CO 1:8">1Ko 1:8</ref></char></note>mulyoke mulonde ekisinga obulungi, olunaku lwa Kristo bwe lulituuka lubasange nga muli balongoofu abataliiko kamogo, <verse number="11" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:11 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JAS 3:18">Yak 3:18</ref></char></note>nga mujjudde ekibala eky’obutuukirivu ku bwa Yesu Kristo, olw’okuweesa Katonda ekitiibwa n’okumutendereza.</para>
  <para style="s1">Obusibe bwa Pawulo bubunyisa Njiri</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>Abooluganda, njagala mmwe mutegeere kaakano nti ebimu ebyambaako byongera bwongezi kubunyisa Njiri, <verse number="13" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:13 </char><char style="xt" closed="false">nny 7, 14, 17</char></note>n’okusibibwa kwange kulyoke kulabise Kristo eri olusiisira lwonna olw’abaserikale ba kabaka n’eri abalala bonna. <verse number="14" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:14 </char><char style="xt" closed="false">nny 7, 13, 17</char></note>N’abooluganda mu Mukama waffe abasinga obungi beeyongedde okuguma olw’okusibibwa kwange, era nga bamaliridde okwaŋŋanga okubuulira nga tebatya.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v"/>Weewaawo abamu bategeeza abantu Kristo lwa buggya na kuvuganya, naye abalala bakikola mu mwoyo mulungi. <verse number="16" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:16 </char><char style="xt" closed="false">nny 7, 12</char></note>Bano bakikola lwa kwagala, kubanga bamanyi nga nalondebwa lwa kulwanirira Njiri. <verse number="17" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:17 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PHP 2:3">Baf 2:3</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false">nny 7, 13, 14</char></note>Naye bali bategeeza Kristo lwa kuvuganya, so si mu mazima, nga balowooza nti banaayongera okunnakuwaza mu busibe bwe ndimu. <verse number="18" style="v"/>Naye nze nfaayo ki? Kristo bw’abuulirwa, mu buli ngeri, oba za bukuusa oba za mazima, nze nsanyuka busanyusi.</para>
  <para style="p">Era nzija kweyongera okusanyuka. <verse number="19" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:19 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2CO 1:11">2Ko 1:11</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 16:7">Bik 16:7</ref></char></note>Kubanga mmanyi nti olw’okunsabira n’olw’amaanyi g’Omwoyo wa Yesu Kristo, ndifuna okulokolebwa kwange. <verse number="20" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:20 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 8:19">Bar 8:19</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false">nny 14 </char><char style="xo" closed="false">c </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CO 6:20">1Ko 6:20</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">d </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 14:8">Bar 14:8</ref></char></note>Neesiga era nsubirira ddala nti sijja kuswala mu nsonga n’emu, wabula ne kaakano nzija kuguma nga bulijjo, Kristo agulumizibwe mu mubiri gwange, oba okuyita mu bulamu oba okuyita mu kufa. <verse number="21" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:21 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="GAL 2:20">Bag 2:20</ref></char></note>Nze mba mulamu lwa Kristo era ne bwe nfa mba ngobolodde. <verse number="22" style="v"/>Naye obanga bwe mba omulamu mu mubiri ng’ekyo kibala ky’okufuba kwange, simanyi kye nnaalondawo. <verse number="23" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:23 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2TI 4:6">2Ti 4:6</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 12:26">Yk 12:26</ref>; <ref loc="2CO 5:8">2Ko 5:8</ref></char></note>Nkwatiddwa buli luuyi; nneegomba okuva mu bulamu buno ŋŋende mbeere ne Kristo, kubanga ekyo kisingako obulungi. <verse number="24" style="v"/>Naye okusigala mu mubiri kye kisinga okwetaagibwa ku lwammwe <verse number="25" style="v"/>Ekyo nkikakasa era nkimanyi nti nzija kuba nga nkyaliwo mbeere nammwe, mulyoke mweyongere okusanyuka n’okukula mu kukkiriza, <verse number="26" style="v"/>bwe ndikomawo gye muli mulyoke mweyongere okwenyumiririza mu Kristo ku lwange.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:27 a </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EPH 4:1">Bef 4:1</ref> </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">b </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1CO 16:13">1Ko 16:13</ref> </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">c </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JUD 1:3">Yud 3</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Naye kirungi obulamu bwammwe bubeerenga nga bwe kisaanira Enjiri ya Kristo; ne bwe ndijja oba ne bwe sirijja kubalaba, mpulire nti muli banywevu era mwegasse mu mwoyo gumu, nga mulwanirira okukkiriza okw’enjiri n’emmeeme emu. <verse number="28" style="v"/>Temutyanga abo ababawakanya kubanga ke kabonero akakakasa nti balizikirizibwa, naye mmwe mulirokolebwa, era ekyo kiva eri Katonda. <verse number="29" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:29 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 5:11">Mat 5:11</ref>, <ref loc="MAT 5:12">12</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 14:22">Bik 14:22</ref></char></note>Kubanga mwaweebwa omukisa, ku lwa Kristo, si mu kumukkiriza kyokka, naye n’okubonaabona ku lulwe. <verse number="30" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:30 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="COL 2:1">Bak 2:1</ref>; <ref loc="1TH 2:2">1Bs 2:2</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 16:19-40">Bik 16:19-40</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">c </char><char style="xt" closed="false">nny 13</char></note>Olutalo lwe mwalaba nga nnwana, era lwe muwulira lwe ndiko kaakano, nammwe lwe muliko.</para>
  <chapter number="2" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Mulabire ku Kristo</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">2:1 a </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="2CO 13:14">2Ko 13:14</ref> </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">b </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="COL 3:12">Bak 3:12</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Kale bwe wabaawo okubazaamu endasi kwonna mu Kristo, oba okusanyusa kwonna okw’okwagala, oba okussa ekimu mu mwoyo, oba okwagala okw’engeri yonna, oba okusaasira, <verse number="2" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:2 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 3:29">Yk 3:29</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PHP 4:2">Baf 4:2</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">c </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 12:16">Bar 12:16</ref></char></note>mutuukirize essanyu lyange, mulowoozenga bumu, nga mulina okwagala, n’omwoyo gumu, nga mulowooza bumu, <verse number="3" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:3 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="GAL 5:26">Bag 5:26</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 12:10">Bar 12:10</ref>; <ref loc="1PE 5:5">1Pe 5:5</ref></char></note>nga temukola kintu na kimu olw’okuvuganya wadde okwewaana okutaliimu, wabula mu bwetoowaze nga buli muntu agulumiza munne okusinga bwe mwegulumiza mwekka, <verse number="4" style="v"/>nga buli muntu tatunuulira bibye yekka, naye ng’afaayo ne ku by’abalala.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">2:5 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 11:29">Mat 11:29</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Mubengamu endowooza eri eyali mu Kristo Yesu,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">2:6 a </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 1:1">Yk 1:1</ref> </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">b </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 5:18">Yk 5:18</ref>
      </char>
    </note>ye newaakubadde nga yali mu kifaananyi kya Katonda,</para>
  <para style="q2">Teyeerowooza kwenkanankana ne Katonda,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">2:7 a </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 20:28">Mat 20:28</ref> </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">b </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 1:14">Yk 1:14</ref>; <ref loc="HEB 2:17">Beb 2:17</ref></char>
    </note>wabula yeewaayo n’afuuka ng’omuddu,</para>
  <para style="q2">era n’azaalibwa ng’omuntu,</para>
  <para style="q2">era n’alabikira mu kifaananyi ky’omuntu,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">2:8 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 26:39">Mat 26:39</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 10:18">Yk 10:18</ref>; <ref loc="HEB 5:8">Beb 5:8</ref></char>
    </note>ne yeetoowaza,</para>
  <para style="q2">n’aba muwulize n’okutuukira ddala ku kufa,</para>
  <para style="q2">ate okufa okw’okukomererwa ku musaalaba.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">2:9 a </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ACT 2:33">Bik 2:33</ref>; <ref loc="HEB 2:9">Beb 2:9</ref> </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">b </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EPH 1:20">Bef 1:20</ref>, <ref loc="EPH 1:21">21</ref></char>
    </note>Katonda kyeyava amugulumiza,</para>
  <para style="q2">n’amuwa erinnya erisinga amannya gonna;</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">2:10 a </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ROM 14:11">Bar 14:11</ref> </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">b </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 28:18">Mat 28:18</ref>
      </char>
    </note>buli vviivi ery’abo abali mu ggulu n’abali ku nsi,</para>
  <para style="q2">era n’abali wansi w’ensi liryoke lifukaamirirenga erinnya lya Yesu,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">2:11 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JHN 13:13">Yk 13:13</ref>
      </char>
    </note>era buli lulimi lwatulenga nga Yesu Kristo ye Mukama,</para>
  <para style="q2">Katonda Kitaffe aweebwe ekitiibwa.</para>
  <para style="s1">Okwakira Ensi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">2:12 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="2CO 7:15">2Ko 7:15</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Noolwekyo abaagalwa, nga bwe muli abawulize bulijjo nga ndi nammwe, kaakano nga bwe siri nammwe mube bawulize nnyo n’okusinga bwe mwali. Munyiikirenga okukola ebiraga nti mwalokolebwa, nga mutya era nga mukankana. <verse number="13" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:13 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EZR 1:5">Ezr 1:5</ref></char></note>Kubanga Katonda yakolera mu mmwe, era yabaagazisa n’abasobozesa okukola by’ayagala, olw’okumusanyusa.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">2:14 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1CO 10:10">1Ko 10:10</ref>; <ref loc="1PE 4:9">1Pe 4:9</ref></char>
    </note>Buli kye mukola mukikolenga awatali kwemulugunya wadde empaka, <verse number="15" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:15 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 5:45">Mat 5:45</ref>, <ref loc="MAT 5:48">48</ref>; <ref loc="EPH 5:1">Bef 5:1</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 2:40">Bik 2:40</ref></char></note>mulyoke mube nga temuliiko kyakunenyezebwa nga muli balongoofu, mube abaana ba Katonda abatalina bbala, wakati mu mulembe ogwakyama era omwonoonefu, mwe mubeere ekyokulabirako eky’amaanyi mu nsi, <verse number="16" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:16 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1TH 2:19">1Bs 2:19</ref></char></note>nga munyweza ekigambo ky’obulamu gye bali, ndyoke mbeere n’eky’okwenyumiriza ku lunaku lwa Kristo, okulaga nti ssaddukira bwereere so ssaateganira busa. <verse number="17" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:17 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2TI 4:6">2Ti 4:6</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 15:16">Bar 15:16</ref></char></note>Naye singa ddala nfukibwa ng’ekiweebwayo ekyokunywa ku ssaddaaka ne ku kuweereza okw’obwakabona okw’okukkiriza kwammwe, nsanyukira wamu nammwe mwenna. <verse number="18" style="v"/>Era nammwe musanyukire wamu nange.</para>
  <para style="s1">Timoseewo ne Epafuladito</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">2:19 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">nny 23</char>
    </note>Mukama waffe Yesu bw’alisiima nsuubira okubatumira mangu Timoseewo, ndyoke ntereere omwoyo nga ntegedde ebibafaako. <verse number="20" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:20 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CO 16:10">1Ko 16:10</ref></char></note>Kubanga tewali mulala alina ndowooza nga yange, <verse number="21" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:21 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CO 10:24">1Ko 10:24</ref>; <ref loc="1CO 13:5">13:5</ref></char></note>kubanga abalala bonna beenoonyeza byabwe ku bwabwe, so si ebya Yesu Kristo. <verse number="22" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:22 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CO 4:17">1Ko 4:17</ref>; <ref loc="1TI 1:2">1Ti 1:2</ref></char></note>Naye ye Timoseewo mumumanyi nga bw’asaanira, kubanga aweerereza wamu nange, ng’omwana bw’akolera awamu ne kitaawe nga tukola omulimu gw’okubuulira Enjiri. <verse number="23" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:23 </char><char style="xt" closed="false">nny 19</char></note>Kale oyo gwe nsuubira okubatumira amangu ddala nga naakamanya nga bwe nnaabeera. <verse number="24" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:24 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PHP 1:25">Baf 1:25</ref></char></note>Naye nkakasa nti Mukama waffe bw’alisiima, nange nze kennyini sirimala bbanga ddene nga sinnajja eyo.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">2:25 a </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PHP 4:3">Baf 4:3</ref> </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">b </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PHM 1:2">Fir 2</ref> </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">c </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PHP 4:18">Baf 4:18</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Era ndabye nga kisaanye okubatumira owooluganda Epafuladito mukozi munnange, era mulwanyi munnange, naye ate nga mutume wammwe, omuweereza ow’eby’obwakabona ow’eby’etaago byange, <verse number="26" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:26 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PHP 1:8">Baf 1:8</ref></char></note>ayagala ennyo okubalaba, mwenna, eyeeraliikirira ennyo olw’obutabalaba, kubanga mwawulira nga yalwala. <verse number="27" style="v"/>Ddala yalwala era yali kumpi n’okufa. Kyokka Katonda yamusaasira, naye era teyasaasira ye yekka, wabula nange yansaasira ennaku n’eteenneeyongera. <verse number="28" style="v"/>Noolwekyo nayagala nnyo okumutuma gye muli mulyoke musanyuke okumulaba nate, ekyo kikendeeze ku nnaku gye nnina. <verse number="29" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:29 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CO 16:18">1Ko 16:18</ref>; <ref loc="1TI 5:17">1Ti 5:17</ref></char></note>Kale mumwanirize nnyo n’essanyu lyonna mu Mukama waffe, era abantu abali ng’oyo mubassangamu ekitiibwa, <verse number="30" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:30 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CO 16:17">1Ko 16:17</ref></char></note>kubanga yabulako katono okufa ng’ali ku mulimu gwa Kristo, ng’akola ebyo bye mwandinkoledde singa mwali nange.</para>
  <chapter number="3" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Obutuukirivu obwa Nnama ddala</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>Ebisigaddeyo, baganda bange, musanyukirenga mu Mukama waffe. Okuddamu ebyo bye nnabawandiikira edda tekunkooya kubanga kyongera kubanyweza. <verse number="2" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:2 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PSA 22:16">Zab 22:16</ref>, <ref loc="PSA 22:20">20</ref></char></note>Mwekuumenga embwa, era mwekuumenga ab’empisa embi, era mwekuumenga abakomola omubiri. <verse number="3" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:3 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 2:28">Bar 2:28</ref>, <ref loc="ROM 2:29">29</ref>; <ref loc="GAL 6:15">Bag 6:15</ref>; <ref loc="COL 2:11">Bak 2:11</ref></char></note>Kubanga ffe bakomole, abasinza Katonda ng’Omwoyo bw’atuluŋŋamya, era twenyumiririza mu Kristo Yesu so tetwesiga mubiri.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>Ne bwe kwandibadde okwesiga omubiri, omuntu omulala yenna bw’alowooza okuba n’obwesige mu mubiri, nze musinga. <verse number="5" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:5 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 1:59">Luk 1:59</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2CO 11:22">2Ko 11:22</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">c </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 11:1">Bar 11:1</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">d </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 23:6">Bik 23:6</ref></char></note>Kubanga nze nakomolebwa ku lunaku olw’omunaana. Ndi Muyisirayiri, ow’omu kika kya Benyamini, Omwebbulaniya wawu, era mu mateeka ndi Mufalisaayo, <verse number="6" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:6 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 8:3">Bik 8:3</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 10:5">Bar 10:5</ref></char></note>eyanyiikira okuyigganya ekkanisa, eyali omutuukirivu mu mateeka, nga siriiko kya kunenyezebwa.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">3:7 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 13:44">Mat 13:44</ref>; <ref loc="LUK 14:33">Luk 14:33</ref></char>
    </note>Naye ebyo byonna ebyali omugabo gye ndi, nabiraba nga butaliimu. <verse number="8" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:8 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EPH 4:13">Bef 4:13</ref>; <ref loc="2PE 1:2">2Pe 1:2</ref></char></note>Naye okusinga byonna, byonna mbiraba ng’okufiirwa, kubanga okutegeera Kristo Yesu Mukama wange, kusinga ebirala byonna. Olwa Kristo nafiirwa ebintu byonna, era mbiraba ng’ebisasiro, ndyoke ngobolole Kristo, <verse number="9" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:9 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 10:5">Bar 10:5</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 9:30">Bar 9:30</ref></char></note>ndabikire mu ye nga sirina butuukirivu bwange ku bwange obuva mu kukwata amateeka, wabula nga nnina obutuukirivu obuva mu kukkiriza Kristo, era obuva eri Katonda obwesigamye ku kukkiriza. <verse number="10" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:10 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 8:17">Bar 8:17</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 6:3-5">Bar 6:3-5</ref></char></note>Njagala okussa ekimu mu bibonoobono bye, nga mmufaanana mu kufa kwe, mmumanye era ntegeere amaanyi g’okuzuukira kwe, <verse number="11" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:11 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="REV 20:5">Kub 20:5</ref>, <ref loc="REV 20:6">6</ref></char></note>nga nsuubira nga nange ndizuukira.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">3:12 a </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1CO 13:10">1Ko 13:10</ref> </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">b </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1TI 6:12">1Ti 6:12</ref> </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">c </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ACT 9:5">Bik 9:5</ref>, <ref loc="ACT 9:6">6</ref></char>
    </note>Sigamba nti mmaze okufuna oba nti mmaze okutuukirira, wabula nfuba okufuna ekyo Kristo Yesu kye yagenderera nfune. <verse number="13" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:13 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 9:62">Luk 9:62</ref></char></note>Abooluganda, mmanyi nti sinnakifuna, naye kye nkola kwe kwerabira ebyo ebiri emabega ne nduubirira ebyo ebiri mu maaso. <verse number="14" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:14 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="HEB 6:1">Beb 6:1</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 8:28">Bar 8:28</ref></char></note>Nduubirira okutuuka awawakanirwa awali empeera ey’okuyita kwa Katonda okwa waggulu mu Kristo Yesu.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">3:15 a </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1CO 2:6">1Ko 2:6</ref> </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">b </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GAL 5:10">Bag 5:10</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Noolwekyo ffe ffenna abatuukiridde ekyo kye tusaana okulowoozanga, naye obanga mulowooza bulala, na kino Katonda alikibabikkulira. <verse number="16" style="v"/>Naye ka tunywerere ku ekyo kye tutuuseeko.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">3:17 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1CO 4:16">1Ko 4:16</ref>; <ref loc="1PE 5:3">1Pe 5:3</ref></char>
    </note>Kale, abooluganda, mwegatte n’abo abangoberera era mugobererenga abo abatambulira mu ebyo bye twabalaga. <verse number="18" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:18 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 20:31">Bik 20:31</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="GAL 6:12">Bag 6:12</ref></char></note>Ekyo newaakubadde nkibabuulidde emirundi emingi, nkiddamu nga nkaaba n’amaziga, nti waliwo abalabe b’omusaalaba gwa Kristo, <verse number="19" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:19 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 16:18">Bar 16:18</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 6:21">Bar 6:21</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">c </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 8:5">Bar 8:5</ref>, <ref loc="ROM 8:6">6</ref></char></note>era ekibalindiridde kwe kuzikirira, kubanga okulya kubafuukidde katonda waabwe, ebyo ebyandibakwasizza ensonyi kye kitiibwa kyabwe era balowooza bintu bya mu nsi. <verse number="20" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:20 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EPH 2:19">Bef 2:19</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="COL 3:1">Bak 3:1</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">c </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CO 1:7">1Ko 1:7</ref></char></note>Kyokka ffe obutaka bwaffe buli mu ggulu, era Omulokozi, Mukama waffe Yesu Kristo, gye tumulindirira okuva. <verse number="21" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:21 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EPH 1:19">Bef 1:19</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CO 15:43-53">1Ko 15:43-53</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">c </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="COL 3:4">Bak 3:4</ref></char></note>Kale bw’alijja emibiri gyaffe gino eminafu egifa aligifuula ng’ogugwe ogw’ekitiibwa, ng’akozesa amaanyi okussa ebintu byonna mu buyinza bwe.</para>
  <chapter number="4" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Okuyigiriza</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PHP 1:8">Baf 1:8</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Kale, baganda bange abaagalwa, era be nnumirirwa omwoyo, mmwe ssanyu lyange era mmwe ngule yange; noolwekyo abaagalwa, muyimirire mu Mukama waffe.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="2" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:2 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PHP 2:2">Baf 2:2</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Ewudiya ne Sintuke mbeegayirira mukkiriziganye mu Mukama waffe. <verse number="3" style="v"/>Era ggwe mukozi munnange, nkusaba oyambenga abakazi abo, kubanga baakolera wamu nange omulimu gw’okubunyisa Enjiri. Abo awamu ne Kerementi, era ne bakozi bannange abalala, amannya gaabwe gawandiikiddwa mu kitabo ky’obulamu.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:4 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ROM 12:12">Bar 12:12</ref>; <ref loc="PHP 3:1">Baf 3:1</ref></char>
    </note>Musanyukirenga mu Mukama waffe bulijjo. Nziramu okubagamba nti musanyukenga. <verse number="5" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:5 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="HEB 10:37">Beb 10:37</ref>; <ref loc="JAS 5:8">Yak 5:8</ref>, <ref loc="JAS 5:9">9</ref></char></note>Era mubeere n’okuzibiikiriza eri abantu bonna. Mukama waffe, ali kumpi. <verse number="6" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:6 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 6:25-34">Mat 6:25-34</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EPH 6:18">Bef 6:18</ref></char></note>Temweraliikiriranga kintu na kimu, wabula mu buli kintu mu kusabanga ne mu kwegayiriranga awamu n’okwebazanga, mutegeezenga Katonda bye mwetaaga. <verse number="7" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:7 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ISA 26:3">Is 26:3</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 14:27">Yk 14:27</ref>; <ref loc="COL 3:15">Bak 3:15</ref></char></note>N’emirembe gya Katonda, egisukkiridde okutegeera kwammwe ginaabakuumanga amagezi gammwe n’emitima gyammwe mu Kristo Yesu.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>Eky’enkomerero, abooluganda, mulowoozenga ku buli kya mazima, na buli ekisiimibwa na buli kya butuukirivu, na buli kirongoofu, na buli kyagalibwa, na buli kyogerwako obulungi, era bwe wabangawo ekirungi oba bwe wabangawo ettendo, ebyo mubirowoozengako. <verse number="9" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:9 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PHP 3:17">Baf 3:17</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 15:33">Bar 15:33</ref></char></note>Ebyo bye mwayiga, n’ebyo bye mwafuna ne muwulira, ebyo mubirowoozengako.</para>
  <para style="s1">Okwebaza</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:10 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="2CO 11:9">2Ko 11:9</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nasanyuka nnyo mu Mukama waffe, kubanga kaakano oluvannyuma lw’ebbanga muzzeemu okundowoozaako buggya, kubanga mwali munzisaako nnyo omwoyo, naye temwalina mukisa ku kiraga. <verse number="11" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:11 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1TI 6:6">1Ti 6:6</ref>, <ref loc="1TI 6:8">8</ref></char></note>Soogera kino olwokubanga Ndiko kye nneetaaga, kubanga mu buli mbeera gye mbaamu nayiga okumalibwanga. <verse number="12" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:12 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CO 4:11">1Ko 4:11</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2CO 11:9">2Ko 11:9</ref></char></note>Mmanyi okubeera nga sirina kantu, era mmanyi okuba nga nnina buli kimu. Mu buli ngeri ne mu bintu byonna nayiga ekyama ekiri mu kukkusibwa ne mu kuba omuyala, mu kuba n’ebingi ne mu bwetaavu. <verse number="13" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:13 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2CO 12:9">2Ko 12:9</ref></char></note>Nnyinza okukola byonna mu oyo ampa amaanyi.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:14 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PHP 1:7">Baf 1:7</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Kyokka mukola bulungi okulumirirwa awamu nange mu kubonaabona kwange. <verse number="15" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:15 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PHP 1:5">Baf 1:5</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2CO 11:8">2Ko 11:8</ref>, <ref loc="2CO 11:9">9</ref></char></note>Mmwe, Abafiripi, mumanyi nti bwe nava e Makedoniya nga nakatandika okubuulira Enjiri, tewali Kkanisa n’emu eyampaayo akantu olw’ebyo bye yafuna okuggyako mmwe mwekka. <verse number="16" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:16 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 17:1">Bik 17:1</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1TH 2:9">1Bs 2:9</ref></char></note>Kubanga ddala ddala bwe nnali mu Sessaloniika mwampeereza emirundi ebiri. <verse number="17" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:17 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CO 9:11">1Ko 9:11</ref>, <ref loc="1CO 9:12">12</ref></char></note>Soogera kino lwa kubanga njagala okufuna ekirabo, wabula kye njagala kwe kulaba ng’ekibala kyeyongera ku lwammwe. <verse number="18" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:18 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PHP 2:25">Baf 2:25</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2CO 2:14">2Ko 2:14</ref></char></note>Naye kaakano nfunye bingi okusinga bye neetaaga, kino kisinzidde mu ebyo bye mwampeereza, Epafuladito bye yandeetera. Biri ng’akaloosa akalungi ennyo aka ssaddaaka esanyusa era esiimibwa Katonda. <verse number="19" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:19 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PSA 23:1">Zab 23:1</ref>; <ref loc="2CO 9:8">2Ko 9:8</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 2:4">Bar 2:4</ref></char></note>Kale ne Katonda wange alibawa buli kye mwetaaga ng’obugagga bwe obungi obuli mu Kristo Yesu bwe buli.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:20 a </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GAL 1:4">Bag 1:4</ref> </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">b </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ROM 11:36">Bar 11:36</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Katonda Kitaffe aweebwenga ekitiibwa emirembe n’emirembe. Amiina.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:21 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GAL 1:2">Bag 1:2</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Munnamusize buli mutukuvu mu Kristo Yesu; era n’abooluganda abali wano nange babalamusizza.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:22 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ACT 9:13">Bik 9:13</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Era n’abatukuvu bonna babatumidde, naye okusingira ddala abo abali mu lubiri lwa Kayisaali.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v"/>Ekisa kya Mukama waffe Yesu Kristo kibeerenga nammwe.</para>
  <para style="p">Amiina.</para>
</usx>
